description.narrative: The situation analysis on children, developed with UNICEF support,;evidenced;progress and challanges towards the achivement of child related SDGs in Tunisia, with six major areas for requiring sustained efforts (SDG1: child poverty rate; SDG2: increasing rates of child overweight; SDG3: risks of epidemics and emerging health issues; SDG4: learning crisis; SDG6: water and hygiene for children; SDG16: violence against children); and complemented by a;review of the equity and efficiency of public expenditures for child related services. The document, together with the UNICEF CPD 2015-2020 evaluation and UN CCA guided the development of the new UNSDCF and UNICEF CPD 2021-25. | Status:Met | As-of Date:05/01/2021
